AUS RENÉ DESCARTES, DIOPTRICE</head> <pb type="VIII_1" n="167"/><head>[Frühjahr – Herbst 1673]</head><div type="ueberlieferung"><p><hi rendition="#b #smaller">Überlieferung:</hi><list><item><label><hi rendition="#i #smaller">L</hi></label>
<p><hi rendition="#smaller">Exzerpt: LH XXXVII 2 Bl. 11. 1 Bl. rechteckig beschnitten, 14 x 6 cm. 4/5 S., Rückseite leer.</hi></p></item><item><label><hi rendition="#i #smaller">Kein Eintrag in KK 1 oder Cc 2.</hi></label>
<p/></item></list></p></div><div type="contents"><p xml:id="Ch20.p4"><hi rendition="#smaller"><hi rendition="#b">Datierungsgründe</hi>: Wir ordnen dieses Stück in das Textcorpus der frühen Auseinandersetzung mit der Cartesischen <ref corresp="#bib_00038"/><hi rendition="#i">La dioptrique</hi> ein und übernehmen die Datierung aus N. 21.</hi></p></div><div type="text"><p xml:id="Ch20.p5"><pb type="L"/><fw type="folNum">[11 r<hi rendition="#sup">o</hi>]</fw> Cartesius<index indexName="Namensregister"><term><hi rendition="#g">Descartes</hi> (Cartesius, des Cartes, Cartes.), René 1596–1650</term></index> quidem in suis <hi rendition="#i">Dioptricis</hi> <app type="Bfootnote"><lem type="main">artic. 22 asserit</lem><note type="lemma-abbrev"><hi rendition="#i">Dioptricis</hi></note><rdg wit="#L" n="1"> ostendit </rdg><rdg wit="#L" n="2"> artic. 22 asserit  <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg></app> <hi rendition="#i">speculum conburens cujus diameter non multo major est centesima circiter parte distantiae quae</hi> <app type="Bfootnote"><lem type="main"><hi rendition="#i">est</hi></lem><rdg wit="#L" cause="addition"><add><hi rendition="#i">est</hi> </add> <note type="editorial"><hi rendition="#i">erg.  L</hi></note></rdg></app> <hi rendition="#i">inter illum locum in quo radios solis colligere debet, id est cujus eadem sit ratio ad hanc distantiam quae diametri solis ad eam quae inter nos et solem licet angeli manu expoliatur non magis calefaciet illum locum in quo radios quam maxime colliget, quam illi radii qui ex nullo speculo reflexi directe a sole manant.</hi><app type="Cfootnote"><lem type="main"/><note type="lemma-abbrev"><hi rendition="#i">manant</hi>.</note><note type="editorial"><hi rendition="#k">R. Descartes,</hi> <bibl corresp="#bib_00037"><hi rendition="#i">Specimina philosophiae</hi>, Amsterdam 1650, Teil 2, S. 168.</bibl></note></app> Memini me aliquando rem considerare <app type="Bfootnote"><lem type="main">et similes quasdam proportiones prodiisse, visam tamen rem</lem><note type="lemma-abbrev">considerare</note><rdg wit="#L" n="1"> et visam rem </rdg><rdg wit="#L" n="2"> et <seg type="apparat-ellipsis"/> rem  <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg></app> paulo latius patere.</p></div></div></body>
